  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Andhra Pradesh</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">AP has three seasons: hot summer (March–May), monsoon (June–September — both southwest and northeast) and a pleasant winter (October–February). October to February is ideal — Tirupati is best in winter, the coastal temples are cool, the deltas are green from monsoon and the Godavari pushkar festival cycle falls in this window.</p>
