{emoji:"🎭",name:"Kuchipudi Dance Festival",location:"Kuchipudi Village, Krishna District",desc:"The annual festival at the birthplace of Kuchipudi classical dance — performed by hereditary Brahmin families who have practiced the art for 400 years. The all-night performances of Bhamakalapam (the story of Satyabhama, played by a man in female role) and other classical pieces are performed in the village square under the stars, exactly as they have been for centuries."},
